org.openimaj.image.text.extraction.swt

Class WordCandidate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.text.extraction.swt.WordCandidate

  • public class WordCandidate
extends Object
    This class models a candidate word (a collection of letter candidates with a consistent inter-character spacing) from the SWTTextDetector.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
